Subject: [PATCH 1/4] dt-bindings: clock: qcom,rpmcc: add MSM8920

Document the "qcom,rpmcc-msm8920" compatible for the RPM clock
controller found on MSM8920.

Signed-off-by: Catherine Frederick (coolguy) <serenity@floorchan.org>
[aneesh: split the binding into its own patch per submitting-patches]
Signed-off-by: Aneesh Pradhan <aneeshpradhan@acm.org>
---
 Documentation/devicetree/bindings/clock/qcom,rpmcc.yaml | 2 ++
 1 file changed, 2 insertions(+)

diff --git a/Documentation/devicetree/bindings/clock/qcom,rpmcc.yaml b/Documentation/devicetree/bindings/clock/qcom,rpmcc.yaml
index ab97d4b..e35a003 100644
--- a/Documentation/devicetree/bindings/clock/qcom,rpmcc.yaml
+++ b/Documentation/devicetree/bindings/clock/qcom,rpmcc.yaml
@@ -32,6 +32,7 @@ properties:
           - qcom,rpmcc-msm8909
           - qcom,rpmcc-msm8916
           - qcom,rpmcc-msm8917
+          - qcom,rpmcc-msm8920
           - qcom,rpmcc-msm8936
           - qcom,rpmcc-msm8937
           - qcom,rpmcc-msm8940
@@ -112,6 +113,7 @@ allOf:
               - qcom,rpmcc-msm8226
               - qcom,rpmcc-msm8916
               - qcom,rpmcc-msm8917
+              - qcom,rpmcc-msm8920
               - qcom,rpmcc-msm8936
               - qcom,rpmcc-msm8937
               - qcom,rpmcc-msm8940

